Q_a_f wa*a*lqur-_a_ni almajeed*i*
Bal AAajiboo an j_a_ahum mun_th_irun minhum faq_a_la alk_a_firoona h_atha_ shay-on AAajeeb*un*
A-i_tha_ mitn_a_ wakunn_a_ tur_a_ban _tha_lika rajAAun baAAeed*un*
Qad AAalimn_a_ m_a_ tanqu_s_u al-ar_d_u minhum waAAindan_a_ kit_a_bun _h_afee\_th_\*un*
Bal ka_thth_aboo bi*a*l_h_aqqi lamm_a_ j_a_ahum fahum fee amrin mareej*in*
Afalam yan\_th_\uroo il_a_ a*l*ssam_a_-i fawqahum kayfa banayn_a_h_a_ wazayyann_a_h_a_ wam_a_ lah_a_ min furooj*in*
Wa*a*l-ar_d_a madadn_a_h_a_ waalqayn_a_ feeh_a_ raw_a_siya waanbatn_a_ feeh_a_ min kulli zawjin baheej*in*
Tab_s_iratan wa_th_ikr_a_ likulli AAabdin muneeb*in*
Wanazzaln_a_ mina a*l*ssam_a_-i m_a_an mub_a_rakan faanbatn_a_ bihi jann_a_tin wa_h_abba al_h_a_s_eed*i*
Wa*al*nnakhla b_a_siq_a_tin lah_a_ _t_alAAun na_d_eed*un*
Rizqan lilAAib_a_di waa_h_yayn_a_ bihi baldatan maytan ka_tha_lika alkhurooj*u*
Ka_thth_abat qablahum qawmu noo_h_in waa_s_-_ha_bu a*l*rrassi wathamood*u*
WaAA_a_dun wafirAAawnu wa-ikhw_a_nu loo_t_*in*
Waa_s_-_ha_bu al-aykati waqawmu tubbaAAin kullun ka_thth_aba a*l*rrusula fa_h_aqqa waAAeed*i*
AfaAAayeen_a_ bi*a*lkhalqi al-awwali bal hum fee labsin min khalqin jadeed*in*
Walaqad khalaqn_a_ al-ins_a_na wanaAAlamu m_a_ tuwaswisu bihi nafsuhu wana_h_nu aqrabu ilayhi min _h_abli alwareed*i*
I_th_ yatalaqq_a_ almutalaqqiy_a_ni AAani alyameeni waAAani a*l*shshim_a_li qaAAeed*un*
M_a_ yalfi\_th_\u min qawlin ill_a_ ladayhi raqeebun AAateed*un*
Waj_a_at sakratu almawti bi*a*l_h_aqqi _tha_lika m_a_ kunta minhu ta_h_eed*u*
Wanufikha fee a*l*_ss_oori _tha_lika yawmu alwaAAeed*i*
Waj_a_at kullu nafsin maAAah_a_ s_a_-iqun washaheed*un*
Laqad kunta fee ghaflatin min h_atha_ fakashafn_a_ AAanka ghi_ta_aka faba_s_aruka alyawma _h_adeed*un*
Waq_a_la qareenuhu h_atha_ m_a_ ladayya AAateed*un*
Alqiy_a_ fee jahannama kulla kaff_a_rin AAaneed*in*
Mann_a_AAin lilkhayri muAAtadin mureeb*in*
Alla_th_ee jaAAala maAAa All_a_hi il_a_han _a_khara faalqiy_a_hu fee alAAa_tha_bi a*l*shshadeed*i*
Q_a_la qareenuhu rabban_a_ m_a_ a_t_ghaytuhu wal_a_kin k_a_na fee _d_al_a_lin baAAeed*in*
Q_a_la l_a_ takhta_s_imoo ladayya waqad qaddamtu ilaykum bi*a*lwaAAeed*i*
M_a_ yubaddalu alqawlu ladayya wam_a_ an_a_ bi\_th_\all_a_min lilAAabeed*i*
Yawma naqoolu lijahannama hali imtala\ti wataqoolu hal min mazeed*in*
Waozlifati aljannatu lilmuttaqeena ghayra baAAeed*in*
H_atha_ m_a_ tooAAadoona likulli aww_a_bin _h_afee\_th_\*in*
Man khashiya a*l*rra_h_m_a_na bi*a*lghaybi waj_a_a biqalbin muneeb*in*
Odkhulooh_a_ bisal_a_min _tha_lika yawmu alkhulood*i*
Lahum m_a_ yash_a_oona feeh_a_ waladayn_a_ mazeed*un*
Wakam ahlakn_a_ qablahum min qarnin hum ashaddu minhum ba_t_shan fanaqqaboo fee albil_a_di hal min ma_h_ee_s_*in*
Inna fee _tha_lika la_th_ikr_a_ liman k_a_na lahu qalbun aw alq_a_ a*l*ssamAAa wahuwa shaheed*un*
Walaqad khalaqn_a_ a*l*ssam_a_w_a_ti wa*a*l-ar_d_a wam_a_ baynahum_a_ fee sittati ayy_a_min wam_a_ massan_a_ min lughoob*in*
Fa*i*_s_bir AAal_a_ m_a_ yaqooloona wasabbi_h_ bi_h_amdi rabbika qabla _t_ulooAAi a*l*shshamsi waqabla alghuroob*i*
Wamina allayli fasabbi_h_hu waadb_a_ra a*l*ssujood*i*
Wa*i*stamiAA yawma yun_a_di almun_a_di min mak_a_nin qareeb*in*
Yawma yasmaAAoona a*l*_ss_ay_h_ata bi*a*l_h_aqqi _tha_lika yawmu alkhurooj*i*
Inn_a_ na_h_nu nu_h_yee wanumeetu wa-ilayn_a_ alma_s_eer*u*
Yawma tashaqqaqu al-ar_d_u AAanhum sir_a_AAan _tha_lika _h_ashrun AAalayn_a_ yaseer*un*
Na_h_nu aAAlamu bim_a_ yaqooloona wam_a_ anta AAalayhim bijabb_a_rin fa_th_akkir bi*a*lqur-_a_ni man yakh_a_fu waAAeed*i*
